 (3,751 m) is a mountain in the Bernina Range in Switzerland. 
<REF ID="660.2" SEMCAT="mountain" SYNCAT="np-subj">
<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="pronoun" CASE="nominative">It</REFEX>
